<!DOCTYPE html><html lang="en" data-theme="light"><head><meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=UTF-8"><link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="cid:css-f409d488-8f9e-4423-9a8b-d468e399efe1@mhtml.blink" />
  
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>RescueRide - Roadside Help</title>
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com/" crossorigin="">
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700;800&amp;display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.5.2/css/all.min.css">
  
</head>
<body>
  <nav class="topbar">
    <div class="brand">
      <div class="brand-badge"><i class="fa-solid fa-truck-medical"></i></div>
      <div>
        <div>RescueRide</div>
        <small style="opacity:.82; font-weight:600;">24/7 roadside support</small>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="nav-actions">
      <button class="nav-btn"><i class="fa-solid fa-user"></i> Login</button>
      <button class="nav-btn" aria-label="Refresh location"><i class="fa-solid fa-location-crosshairs"></i></button>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <main class="shell">
    <section class="hero">
      <div class="hero-card">
        <div class="tag"><i class="fa-solid fa-bolt"></i> Fast help near your live location</div>
        <h1>Roadside rescue with current location, OTP login, fuel, towing, mechanic and battery support.</h1>
        <p>RescueRide includes live location tracking, a login form with name, mobile number, OTP and current location, plus dedicated service sections for mechanic problems, fuel delivery, towing support and battery jump start requests.</p>
        <div class="hero-pills">
          <div class="pill">Live GPS location</div>
          <div class="pill">OTP sign-in</div>
          <div class="pill">Mechanic diagnosis</div>
          <div class="pill">Fuel request</div>
          <div class="pill">Towing support</div>
          <div class="pill">Battery jump</div>
        </div>
        <div class="hero-actions">
          <button class="btn btn-primary"><i class="fa-solid fa-screwdriver-wrench"></i> Choose service</button>
          <button class="btn btn-light"><i class="fa-solid fa-layer-group"></i> Open pages</button>
          <button class="btn btn-danger"><i class="fa-solid fa-triangle-exclamation"></i> Emergency SOS</button>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="hero-side">
        <div class="panel">
          <div class="page-header">
            <div>
              <h3>Current &amp; live location</h3>
              <p class="small-note">Auto-detects your position and keeps the service team updated.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="live-dot">Live</div>
          </div>
          <div class="mini-map" aria-hidden="true">
            <div class="map-line"></div>
            <div class="map-rider"></div>
            <div class="map-pin"></div>
          </div>
          <div class="location-grid">
            <div class="metric"><span>Current location</span><strong id="locationText">Lat 12.97160, Lng 77.59460</strong></div>
            <div class="metric"><span>Coordinates</span><strong id="coordsText">12.97160, 77.59460</strong></div>
            <div class="metric"><span>Area type</span><strong id="areaTypeText">Serviceable urban zone</strong></div>
            <div class="metric"><span>Last update</span><strong id="lastUpdatedText">09:41:43</strong></div>
          </div>
          <div style="display:flex; gap:10px; flex-wrap:wrap; margin-top:16px;">
            <button class="btn btn-primary"><i class="fa-solid fa-rotate"></i> Refresh location</button>
            <button class="btn btn-light"><i class="fa-solid fa-satellite-dish"></i> <span id="liveBtnText">Start live tracking</span></button>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="servicesSection" class="services-section">
      <div class="page-header">
        <div>
          <h2 class="section-title">Service cards</h2>
          <p class="small-note">Each service opens with the exact details customers usually need during breakdowns.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="tag"><i class="fa-solid fa-clock"></i> Avg response 15 to 40 min</div>
      </div>

      <div class="services-grid">
        <article class="service-card">
          <div class="service-icon bg-mechanic"><i class="fa-solid fa-wrench"></i></div>
          <h3>Mechanic service</h3>
          <p>Select the problem and send a clear request like puncture, engine not starting, brake issue, clutch issue, overheating or chain problem.</p>
          <div class="service-meta"><span><i class="fa-regular fa-clock"></i> 15-30 min</span><span><i class="fa-solid fa-user-gear"></i> Verified mechanic</span></div>
          <a href="https://d2z0o16i8xm8ak.cloudfront.net/web/direct-files/347046955881727a2c9073543f4521fd/9e54ccaa-bdd6-4d23-9633-1843a27899a8/b624a0a1.html?__&amp;Signature=RM8qKrdpdm14Ywjw05GgOGpRBFSTNf2QqD7s71AxQBts3S9QjVGEtz06ms7rawrV7lg5lu-UkVIRTq7zyQRkL4Lz36eWbRBnkyKRqIdLNmMB7TGWsy579Lv5EU2A7iFywBHX7YG377s2P4wJGI7O-yoGnjA5UA9pP988bqF4wje7lM3eFKMHkfqJzguCPK2jfcs2nFxWuYIqp4ioXepdB7OlN8A5Cpi-7tri~3Cec3~b-BmhPH56nLSt9pcYCeF9QYPW0kLUX7WIFOjDp8saVWKbGvsoX17UMZkH2tGqNN4bAtJRc1xPiOSVnJ8A25cA0vdzqExmLpvLnap9KCwUBA__&amp;Key-Pair-Id=K1BF7XGXAIMYNX&amp;rnd=1777435897856&amp;utm_source=perplexity#mechanicPage" class="btn btn-primary">Open mechanic page</a>
        </article>

        <article class="service-card">
          <div class="service-icon bg-fuel"><i class="fa-solid fa-gas-pump"></i></div>
          <h3>Fuel page login</h3>
          <p>A dedicated fuel page lets users enter name, mobile, OTP, current location, fuel type and required quantity before dispatch.</p>
          <div class="service-meta"><span><i class="fa-regular fa-clock"></i> 20-30 min</span><span><i class="fa-solid fa-oil-can"></i> Petrol or diesel</span></div>
          <a href="https://d2z0o16i8xm8ak.cloudfront.net/web/direct-files/347046955881727a2c9073543f4521fd/9e54ccaa-bdd6-4d23-9633-1843a27899a8/b624a0a1.html?__&amp;Signature=RM8qKrdpdm14Ywjw05GgOGpRBFSTNf2QqD7s71AxQBts3S9QjVGEtz06ms7rawrV7lg5lu-UkVIRTq7zyQRkL4Lz36eWbRBnkyKRqIdLNmMB7TGWsy579Lv5EU2A7iFywBHX7YG377s2P4wJGI7O-yoGnjA5UA9pP988bqF4wje7lM3eFKMHkfqJzguCPK2jfcs2nFxWuYIqp4ioXepdB7OlN8A5Cpi-7tri~3Cec3~b-BmhPH56nLSt9pcYCeF9QYPW0kLUX7WIFOjDp8saVWKbGvsoX17UMZkH2tGqNN4bAtJRc1xPiOSVnJ8A25cA0vdzqExmLpvLnap9KCwUBA__&amp;Key-Pair-Id=K1BF7XGXAIMYNX&amp;rnd=1777435897856&amp;utm_source=perplexity#fuelPage" class="btn btn-primary">Open fuel page</a>
        </article>

        <article class="service-card">
          <div class="service-icon bg-towing"><i class="fa-solid fa-truck-pickup"></i></div>
          <h3>Towing service</h3>
          <p>Users can request towing by entering vehicle type, destination workshop, wheel condition and whether the vehicle is safely movable.</p>
          <div class="service-meta"><span><i class="fa-regular fa-clock"></i> 25-40 min</span><span><i class="fa-solid fa-road"></i> Long-distance support</span></div>
          <a href="https://d2z0o16i8xm8ak.cloudfront.net/web/direct-files/347046955881727a2c9073543f4521fd/9e54ccaa-bdd6-4d23-9633-1843a27899a8/b624a0a1.html?__&amp;Signature=RM8qKrdpdm14Ywjw05GgOGpRBFSTNf2QqD7s71AxQBts3S9QjVGEtz06ms7rawrV7lg5lu-UkVIRTq7zyQRkL4Lz36eWbRBnkyKRqIdLNmMB7TGWsy579Lv5EU2A7iFywBHX7YG377s2P4wJGI7O-yoGnjA5UA9pP988bqF4wje7lM3eFKMHkfqJzguCPK2jfcs2nFxWuYIqp4ioXepdB7OlN8A5Cpi-7tri~3Cec3~b-BmhPH56nLSt9pcYCeF9QYPW0kLUX7WIFOjDp8saVWKbGvsoX17UMZkH2tGqNN4bAtJRc1xPiOSVnJ8A25cA0vdzqExmLpvLnap9KCwUBA__&amp;Key-Pair-Id=K1BF7XGXAIMYNX&amp;rnd=1777435897856&amp;utm_source=perplexity#towingPage" class="btn btn-primary">Open towing page</a>
        </article>

        <article class="service-card">
          <div class="service-icon bg-battery"><i class="fa-solid fa-car-battery"></i></div>
          <h3>Battery jump services</h3>
          <p>Battery support captures the issue, checks whether headlights work and requests jump-start, testing or replacement visit.</p>
          <div class="service-meta"><span><i class="fa-regular fa-clock"></i> 15-25 min</span><span><i class="fa-solid fa-bolt"></i> Jump start available</span></div>
          <a href="https://d2z0o16i8xm8ak.cloudfront.net/web/direct-files/347046955881727a2c9073543f4521fd/9e54ccaa-bdd6-4d23-9633-1843a27899a8/b624a0a1.html?__&amp;Signature=RM8qKrdpdm14Ywjw05GgOGpRBFSTNf2QqD7s71AxQBts3S9QjVGEtz06ms7rawrV7lg5lu-UkVIRTq7zyQRkL4Lz36eWbRBnkyKRqIdLNmMB7TGWsy579Lv5EU2A7iFywBHX7YG377s2P4wJGI7O-yoGnjA5UA9pP988bqF4wje7lM3eFKMHkfqJzguCPK2jfcs2nFxWuYIqp4ioXepdB7OlN8A5Cpi-7tri~3Cec3~b-BmhPH56nLSt9pcYCeF9QYPW0kLUX7WIFOjDp8saVWKbGvsoX17UMZkH2tGqNN4bAtJRc1xPiOSVnJ8A25cA0vdzqExmLpvLnap9KCwUBA__&amp;Key-Pair-Id=K1BF7XGXAIMYNX&amp;rnd=1777435897856&amp;utm_source=perplexity#batteryPage" class="btn btn-primary">Open battery page</a>
        </article>
      </div>

      <div class="route-banner">
        <div>
          <strong id="routeText">Nearest rescue partner will route to Lat 12.97160, Lng 77.59460 after dispatch confirmation.</strong>
          <div class="small-note" style="color: rgba(255,255,255,0.82); margin-top:6px;">Mechanic, fuel van, towing truck and battery team all use the same live tracking module.</div>
        </div>
        <button class="btn btn-light"><i class="fa-solid fa-location-arrow"></i> Update route</button>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="loginSection" class="auth-grid">
      <div class="form-card">
        <div class="page-header">
          <div>
            <h2 class="section-title">Login page</h2>
            <p class="small-note">Add name, mobile number, OTP and current location before requesting help.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="tag"><i class="fa-solid fa-mobile-screen-button"></i> Secure OTP</div>
        </div>
        <form>
          <div class="input-group">
            <label for="userName">Full name</label>
            <input id="userName" type="text" placeholder="Enter your name" required="">
          </div>
          <div class="input-group">
            <label for="mobileNumber">Mobile number</label>
            <input id="mobileNumber" type="tel" placeholder="Enter 10-digit number" pattern="[0-9]{10}" required="">
          </div>
          <div class="input-group">
            <label for="otpNumber">OTP verification</label>
            <div class="otp-row">
              <input id="otpNumber" type="text" placeholder="Enter OTP" required="">
              <button type="button" class="btn btn-light">Send OTP</button>
            </div>
            <div class="small-note" id="otpStatus">Click send OTP to get a demo code.</div>
          </div>
          <div class="input-group">
            <label for="currentLocationInput">Current location</label>
            <div class="otp-row">
              <input id="currentLocationInput" type="text" placeholder="Use current GPS location" required="">
              <button type="button" class="btn btn-light">Use current</button>
            </div>
          </div>
          <button class="btn btn-primary" type="submit"><i class="fa-solid fa-right-to-bracket"></i> Login &amp; continue</button>
        </form>
      </div>

      <div class="timeline-card">
        <h2 class="section-title">How it works</h2>
        <div class="timeline">
          <div class="step"><div class="step-badge">1</div><div><strong>Share location</strong><div class="small-note">The app detects your current location and keeps updating it as live location if you enable tracking.</div></div></div>
          <div class="step"><div class="step-badge">2</div><div><strong>Verify with OTP</strong><div class="small-note">Demo OTP is generated inside the site so you can test the login flow quickly.</div></div></div>
          <div class="step"><div class="step-badge">3</div><div><strong>Select your issue</strong><div class="small-note">Choose mechanic, fuel, towing or battery support and fill only the details relevant to that problem.</div></div></div>
          <div class="step"><div class="step-badge">4</div><div><strong>Track rescue partner</strong><div class="small-note">A live status area confirms the current location, last update time and selected service route.</div></div></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="pagesSection" class="page-grid">
      <div id="mechanicPage" class="page-card">
        <div class="page-header">
          <div>
            <h2 class="section-title">Mechanic service page</h2>
            <p class="small-note">Tell us what is the problem so the right mechanic and tools are sent.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="tag"><i class="fa-solid fa-screwdriver-wrench"></i> Service diagnosis</div>
        </div>
        <form>
          <div class="input-group">
            <label for="vehicleType">Vehicle type</label>
            <select id="vehicleType" required="">
              <option value="">Select vehicle</option>
              <option>Bike</option>
              <option>Car</option>
              <option>Scooter</option>
              <option>Auto</option>
              <option>Other</option>
            </select>
          </div>
          <div class="input-group">
            <label for="mechanicProblem">What is the problem?</label>
            <select id="mechanicProblem" required="">
              <option value="">Choose problem</option>
              <option>Engine not starting</option>
              <option>Puncture</option>
              <option>Brake issue</option>
              <option>Clutch issue</option>
              <option>Overheating</option>
              <option>Chain or belt issue</option>
            </select>
          </div>
          <div class="input-group">
            <label for="mechanicNotes">Extra notes</label>
            <textarea id="mechanicNotes" placeholder="Describe sound, smoke, warning lights or visible issue"></textarea>
          </div>
          <button class="btn btn-primary" type="submit">Book mechanic</button>
        </form>
      </div>

      <div id="fuelPage" class="page-card">
        <div class="page-header">
          <div>
            <h2 class="section-title">Fuel service page</h2>
            <p class="small-note">Request fuel delivery with your live location and exact quantity.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="tag"><i class="fa-solid fa-gas-pump"></i> Fuel dispatch</div>
        </div>
        <form>
          <div class="input-group">
            <label for="fuelName">Full name</label>
            <input id="fuelName" type="text" placeholder="Enter your name" required="">
          </div>
          <div class="input-group">
            <label for="fuelMobile">Mobile number</label>
            <input id="fuelMobile" type="tel" placeholder="Enter 10-digit number" pattern="[0-9]{10}" required="">
          </div>
          <div class="input-group">
            <label for="fuelOtp">OTP</label>
            <input id="fuelOtp" type="text" placeholder="Enter OTP" required="">
          </div>
          <div class="input-group">
            <label for="fuelLocation">Current location</label>
            <input id="fuelLocation" type="text" placeholder="Detected location or manual entry" required="">
          </div>
          <div class="input-group">
            <label for="fuelType">Fuel type</label>
            <select id="fuelType" required="">
              <option value="">Select fuel type</option>
              <option>Petrol</option>
              <option>Diesel</option>
            </select>
          </div>
          <div class="input-group">
            <label for="fuelQuantity">Required quantity</label>
            <input id="fuelQuantity" type="text" placeholder="Example: 5 liters" required="">
          </div>
          <button class="btn btn-primary" type="submit">Request fuel</button>
        </form>
      </div>

      <div id="towingPage" class="page-card">
        <div class="page-header">
          <div>
            <h2 class="section-title">Towing service page</h2>
            <p class="small-note">Share vehicle condition and destination so the towing team arrives prepared.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="tag"><i class="fa-solid fa-truck-pickup"></i> Towing support</div>
        </div>
        <form>
          <div class="input-group">
            <label for="towVehicle">Vehicle type</label>
            <select id="towVehicle" required="">
              <option value="">Select vehicle</option>
              <option>Bike</option>
              <option>Car</option>
              <option>SUV</option>
              <option>Van</option>
              <option>Other</option>
            </select>
          </div>
          <div class="input-group">
            <label for="towCondition">Wheel condition</label>
            <select id="towCondition" required="">
              <option value="">Select condition</option>
              <option>All wheels okay</option>
              <option>One wheel damaged</option>
              <option>Multiple wheels damaged</option>
              <option>Axle issue</option>
            </select>
          </div>
          <div class="input-group">
            <label for="towMovable">Is the vehicle movable?</label>
            <select id="towMovable" required="">
              <option value="">Choose option</option>
              <option>Yes, but unsafe to drive</option>
              <option>No, completely immobilized</option>
            </select>
          </div>
          <div class="input-group">
            <label for="towDestination">Destination workshop</label>
            <input id="towDestination" type="text" placeholder="Workshop or drop location" required="">
          </div>
          <button class="btn btn-primary" type="submit">Request towing</button>
        </form>
      </div>

      <div id="batteryPage" class="page-card">
        <div class="page-header">
          <div>
            <h2 class="section-title">Battery jump service page</h2>
            <p class="small-note">Tell us whether the issue needs a jump start, testing or replacement visit.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="tag"><i class="fa-solid fa-car-battery"></i> Battery support</div>
        </div>
        <form>
          <div class="input-group">
            <label for="batteryIssue">Issue type</label>
            <select id="batteryIssue" required="">
              <option value="">Select issue</option>
              <option>Car not starting</option>
              <option>Weak ignition</option>
              <option>Need jump start</option>
              <option>Need battery testing</option>
              <option>Need replacement visit</option>
            </select>
          </div>
          <div class="input-group">
            <label for="headlightCheck">Do headlights turn on?</label>
            <select id="headlightCheck" required="">
              <option value="">Choose option</option>
              <option>Yes</option>
              <option>No</option>
              <option>Dim lights only</option>
            </select>
          </div>
          <div class="input-group">
            <label for="batteryNotes">Extra notes</label>
            <textarea id="batteryNotes" placeholder="Mention dashboard lights, clicking sound or recent battery issues"></textarea>
          </div>
          <button class="btn btn-primary" type="submit">Request battery help</button>
        </form>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <footer>
    RescueRide demo page for roadside assistance bookings with location, OTP login and support workflows.
  </footer>

  


</body></html>
